    {
      "type": "text", "id": "scope_t", "x": 100, "y": 242, "width": 204, "height": 88,
      "text": "1 · EXPLICIT SCOPE\nwhat the agent can touch.\nfile system, DB perms,\ntool registry, network\nboundaries — shrinks the\naction space",
      "originalText": "1 · EXPLICIT SCOPE\nwhat the agent can touch.\nfile system, DB perms,\ntool registry, network\nboundaries — shrinks the\naction space",
