    {
      "type": "text", "id": "drop", "x": 86, "y": 400, "width": 780, "height": 32,
      "text": "Drop any one and you get a partial solution: scope without contract = in-bounds\nbut aimless · contract without adversarial eval = sycophantic self-grading.",
